IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Bridget Anne DRENTER and John Drenter Upon the Petition of Bridget Anne Drenter, Petitioner-Appellant/Cross-Appellee, And Concerning John Drenter, Respondent-Appellee/Cross-Appellant. No. 17-1548 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed February 6, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A husband and wife appeal the decree dissolving their marriage. AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED AND REMANDED.

AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED. REMANDED.
